series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: Liv (Rose McIver) and Clive (Malcolm Goodwin) investigate the murder of a journalist working on a story linking psychotic episodes in a small number of consumers to the energy drink Max Rager. Liv goes straight to the top at Max Rager HQ and questions the man in charge, Vaughn Du Clark (guest-star Steven Weber). Meanwhile, Ravi (Rahul Kohli) tries to help Major (Robert Buckley) who continues to believe he's going crazy.
name: Mr. Berserk

description: After rescuing Princess Orangutan from Daddy-sad-heads, Finn & Jake head to a post-apocalyptic water park for a day of fun.
name: Water Park Prank
Taking a Break From All Your Worries
Islanded in a Stream of Stars
A Lighthouse in the Sea of Time

description:
Original English and Japanese title:

English: I Will Defeat Freeza... The Mysterious Youth Awaiting Goku

Japanese: Furīza wa Boku ga Taosu... Gokū o Matsu Nazo no Shōnen (フリーザはボクが倒す…悟空を待つ謎の少年)

The Earth faces its darkest hour as Frieza and his father King Cold rapidly approach! Without Goku to assist them, the Z-Fighters prepare to launch a desperate attack against the most powerful evil the universe has ever known!
name: The Mysterious Youth

description:
Original English and Japanese title:

English: Freeza Halved by a Single Stroke!! Another Super Saiyan

Japanese: Furīza o Ittō Ryōdan!! Mō Hitori no Sūpā Saiyajin (フリーザを一刃両断!!もう一人の超サイヤ人)

Frieza and King Cold descend upon the Earth, but a mysterious warrior has come to thwart their diabolical plot for revenge. Does this brash young hero have what it takes to stand up to these twin titans of evil?
name: Another Super Saiyan?

description: The crew of Serenity pulls off a train job for a crime boss, but the circumstances change drastically when they discover that the cargo they are supposed to be stealing is disparately needed medicine for a colony.
name: The Train Job

description: As the crew of Serenity comes across a mysterious empty space-ship floating through space they discover one survivor, who may not be all that healthy, but when a alliance ship turns up and search's their ship looking for River and Simon.
name: Bushwhacked

description: When someone close to Major (Robert Buckley) dies of an apparent suicide, Liv (Rose McIver) consumes the brains, resulting in a mix of reality and paranoia. Clive (Malcolm Goodwin) questions Major and learns of a secret computer file that may contain important details in the investigation -- and finding the killer.
name: Astroburger

deck: Ravi may have found a cure for the zombie state. Meanwhile Liv gets closer to killing Blaine, unfortunately so does Major Lilywhite.
name: Dead Rat, Live Rat, Brown Rat, White Rat

description: Malcom attempts to pull a smuggling job at a society dance that Irana is attending, only to get himself into a death match with her 'date'.
name: Shindig

description: Finn and Jake storm Magic Man's house to rescue his new apprentice.
name: You Forgot Your Floaties

description: A fed-up Lumpy Space Princess leaves the woods for a glamorous career in babysitting.
name: Be Sweet
